                                <div class="number"><span>03</span></div>
                                <div class="detail-box">
                                    <h5 class="color-red">Be Innovative</h5>
                                    <p>Innovation is at the heart of Binaro, from the spark of a new idea, developing cutting-edge digital solutions, to creativity in originality. We believe in our ability to move boundaries for the benefit and delight of our clients and team members, as well as for our other stakeholders.</p>
                                    <h6>Ask yourself:</h6>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>What helps you to have innovative or creative ideas?</li>
                                        <li>What innovative ideas do you have that perhaps you haven’t spoken up about?</li>
                                        <li>How do you express your ideas to your team members and clients?</li>
                                        <li>How do you encourage your team members in sharing their innovative or creative ideas?</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
