                                <div class="number"><span>04</span></div>
                                <div class="detail-box">
                                    <h5 class="color-dark-blue">embrace challenge</h5>
                                    <p>There are challenges and hurdles that are encountered in every company. The philosophy of Binaro is to welcome and face challenges head-on, not to shy away in the face of adversity. Embodying a growth mindset, we utilize our skillsets to tackle any tasks, however challenging they may be. We believe in overcoming any challenges effectively, to learn and grow continuously to be prepared in facing even more ambitious future challenges.</p>
                                    <h6>Ask yourself:</h6>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>How do you recognize and face your challenges?</li>
                                        <li>How do you find applicable solutions?</li>
                                        <li>How do you support your team members to deal with their challenges?</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
