                                <div class="detail-box">
                                    <h5 class="color-cyan">be honest</h5>
                                    <p>Honesty is a fundamental pillar of Binaro. Only in being transparent about our progress and timelines, we can enable trust from clients and team members alike. We are constantly feeding back to all parties that we work with. Our communication is open and honest.</p>
                                    <h6>Ask yourself:</h6>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>How do you express honesty with clients and within your team?</li>
                                        <li>How can you improve communication?</li>
                                    </ul>
