                                <div class="number"><span>06</span></div>
                                <div class="detail-box">
                                    <h5 class="color-green">work smart</h5>
                                    <p>Time is the most valuable asset. We believe that working smart using effective time management, foresight and task scheduling increases productivity. By working smart in facing countless tasks, we can overcome them and deliver high-quality results on time to our clients.</p>
                                    <h6>Ask yourself:</h6>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>What do you understand about working smart?</li>
                                        <li>What can you do to work smart and enhance productivity?</li>
                                        <li>How do you support team members in working smart?</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
