                                <div class="number"><span>07</span></div>
                                <div class="detail-box">
                                    <h5 class="color-light-blue">do it right, do it once</h5>
                                    <p>Binaro does things right to only do it once. We all make mistakes, but we grow and learn from them, to avoid making the same mistakes. By sharing what we have learnt with others, we support each other through tasks and challenges. There is always room for improvement in what we do, and we keep riding on our learning curve together.</p>
                                    <h6>Ask yourself:</h6>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>How do you prepare for a task to do it right?</li>
                                        <li>What are the control measures that you take to ensure that you are getting it right?</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
