                                <div class="number"><span>08</span></div>
                                <div class="detail-box">
                                    <h5 class="color-red">love what we do</h5>
                                    <p>We love what we do! We feel satisfied whether completing minute tasks or delivering big projects. We are proud to say that this is our work and to share this love with those that are part of our Binaro family.</p>
                                    <h6>Ask yourself:</h6>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>What do you love about your work?</li>
                                        <li>How do you express your love for what you do through work?</li>
                                        <li>How do you recognize love for what we do in your team members?</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
