                                <div class="detail-box">
                                    <h5 class="color-dark-blue">embody team spirit</h5>
                                    <p>We are not Binaro without our team spirit and our teamwork culture. Everyone is an equal and valuable team member that delivers for Binaro. We rely on each other, promote unity and support, and encourage a positive spirit within ourselves and one another. As team members, we listen openly to the suggestions and opinions of others and garner feedback from everyone in our Binaro family. All of us have skillsets to contribute to our projects. Recognizing our team’s strengths and weaknesses allow us to delegate tasks effectively for high-quality and on time project completion.</p>
                                    <h6>Ask yourself:</h6>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>What does team spirit mean to you?</li>
                                        <li>How do you live team spirit?</li>
                                        <li>How do you support teamwork?</li>
                                        <li>How do you foster inclusion in your team?</li>
                                        <li>How do you address issues or critics in your team?</li>
                                    </ul>
