                                    <h5 class="color-cyan">be passionate</h5>
                                    <p>Binaro was built with passion. We are all unique in how our passion led us to Binaro, whether it is our desire to develop a unique customized software application, or through sharing our digital intellect with others. Passion is the driving force of what we do and keeps us and those around us striving to move boundaries.</p>
                                    <h6>Ask yourself:</h6>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>How How do you express your passion in your work?</li>
